The paper discusses virtual network service composition and maintenance, which is a topic related to computer networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the management of virtual network embedding (VNE), network function virtualization service chaining (NFV-SC), and traffic engineering (TE), which are topics related to distributed computing and systems (cs.DC) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel algorithm for solving the constrained shortest path problem, which is a topic related to computational complexity (cs.CC). Finally, the paper discusses the energy efficiency of virtual network services, which is a topic related to social and information networks (cs.SI).
